channel.title: Respawn-Pk Final version || Webclient ready || Great stability
channel.description:
[size=18pt]I don't recommend this source. It's sort of old and there are better sources out today. If you choose though, you can of course use this.[/size] [img]http://img266.imageshack.us/img266/7852/respawnpkbanner.png[/img] Welcome to my FINAL Release of Respawn-Pk V3! ~Why are you Releasing this?~ I was hosting this and just couldn't afford my Vps and Webhost. So I have no other use for the server. Also im not done coding im just done with Respawn-pk i want to start fresh. -What I did- Woodcutting is basicly perfect just missing a few trees. -Trees drop nests- Bone crusher. - When a bone is dropped by an npc if the Bone crusher is in your inventory it burys it automatically. Good mining base. - Random uncuts. People could no clip and smuggle in Dungeoneering, Fixed. - I also fixed the first floor and made the door passable. I made the server a pk server (Not a spawn) - If you want to fix this just change the starter package. Changed home to edge. Fixed mem leaks. Made some shops fit the pk server. - Ex: Dharok in the shops. Removed Funpk because people would die and lose items, I started to fix it. When you kill another player you get 10 Pkp. - Yes I did increase prices in pkp shop. There is a decent Castle Wars base for you to work with, I have bandages doors and waiting room done so far. Implemented Vote4cash. - If you have the mysql part done on your webhost all you have to do is go to client.java and look for
String urlString = ("http://respawnpk.com/vote.php?type=checkvote&username="+playerName);
Just change the
http://respawnpk.com/vote.php
to your vote page. Everything else is setup, make sure you changed the ::vote4cash in your client to your vote page aswell. Much more just cant remember. -Media- [IMG]http://img805.imageshack.us/img805/6840/respawnpk6.png[/img] [IMG]http://img190.imageshack.us/img190/1503/respawnpk5.png[/img] [IMG]http://img847.imageshack.us/img847/1476/respawnpk4.png[/img] [IMG]http://img534.imageshack.us/img534/3708/respawnpk3.png[/img] [IMG]http://img257.imageshack.us/img257/6106/respawnpk2.png[/img] [IMG]http://img163.imageshack.us/img163/1456/respawnpk1.png[/img] Downloads : Server Package (Cache,Source,Client) : [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?q47bvvwixi475x3]http://www.mediafire.com/?q47bvvwixi475x3[/url] Support us! [IMG]http://img839.imageshack.us/img839/7008/rspkimg.png[/img]
